Comment: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,OP「あの光」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:33.63,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}きっとそう僕たちは　太古の時代から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:40.89,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}引き寄せられる　運命だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:44.64,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}宇宙は　知ってただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:48.90,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の　愛の誕生を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:56.78,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}深い海の底　1つの命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:00.24,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あの光は何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:04.29,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}これから未来が　どうなるか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:07.79,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}誰にも分からないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:12.05,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}それでも　どこかに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:15.80,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}いつも光が見えて来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:19.55,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}それは遠い宇宙からの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:23.06,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}希望のような星の輝き
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:27.10,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}何を語っているのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.19,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夜明けまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:36.86,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢よ　覚めるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:44.00,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あの光は何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:33.63,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我们一定是  自太古时代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:40.89,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就命中注定  要相伴相随
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:44.64,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}宇宙  早已知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:48.90,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球  爱的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:56.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}深海底部的一条生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:00.24,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}那道光是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:04.29,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}未来会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:07.79,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}谁也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:12.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便如此  也还是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:15.80,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}总能在某处看见光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:19.55,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}那是来自遥远宇宙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:23.06,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}仿佛希望之星的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:27.10,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}是在诉说些什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.19,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}在黎明到来前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:36.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}梦啊  不要醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:44.00,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}那道光是什么？
Comment: 0,0:25:19.96,0:25:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「YESとNOの間に」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:22.96,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.22,0:25:37.77,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}窓の外は青い空と夏の太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.39,0:25:43.06,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}授業中の教室は淀んだ空気で
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.61,0:25:48.11,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}今の僕がやらなければいけないことは
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.11,0:25:53.37,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}違う世界の風を入れることだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.70,0:25:58.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}答えはわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.83,0:26:02.63,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}自分が信じるもの　手掛かりに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.63,0:26:04.29,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}手掛かりに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.29,0:26:08.80,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}好きなように生きたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.80,0:26:14.76,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}そうだ今から何か始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.76,0:26:16.89,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}よっしゃー行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.89,0:26:19.35,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}YES NO{\fscx20}　{\fscx100}の選択肢じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.35,0:26:22.06,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}進めないよ　ホントの道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.06,0:26:27.23,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}誰かに与えられた地図は邪魔になる
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.23,0:26:29.82,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}YES NO{\fscx20}　{\fscx100}のその間に
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.82,0:26:32.45,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}次の道が生まれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.45,0:26:36.62,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}考えるより立ち上がれ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.62,0:26:42.37,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}夢に向かって走り出せ
Comment: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:22.96,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.22,0:25:37.77,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}窗户外碧空如洗 夏日炎炎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.39,0:25:43.06,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}教室里课堂上 却死气沉沉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.61,0:25:48.11,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}此刻我必须做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.11,0:25:53.37,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}是引入不同世界的风
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.70,0:25:58.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}答案尚不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.83,0:26:02.63,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}那就把自己相信的 当做线索
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.63,0:26:04.29,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}当做线索
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.29,0:26:08.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}想要随心所欲生活
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.80,0:26:14.76,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}那就从现在开始做些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.76,0:26:16.89,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}好 说做就做
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.89,0:26:19.35,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}在{\fscx20}　{\fscx100}YES{\fscx20}　{\fscx100}或{\fscx20}　{\fscx100}NO{\fscx20}　{\fscx100}的选项中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.35,0:26:22.06,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}无法前往真正的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.06,0:26:27.23,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}别人给予的地图反而会帮倒忙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.23,0:26:29.82,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}在{\fscx20}　{\fscx100}YES{\fscx20}　{\fscx100}和{\fscx20}　{\fscx100}NO{\fscx20}　{\fscx100}之间
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.82,0:26:32.45,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}会诞生全新的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.45,0:26:36.62,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}与其思考不如立刻起身
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.62,0:26:42.37,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fax-0.2}朝着梦想迈步奔跑吧
